# Local-only runtime data. The ``*`` (not ``/``) patterns below
# ignore the *contents* of these directories while still allowing
# the directory itself (with a ``.gitkeep`` placeholder) to be
# tracked. That way ``git clone`` produces the empty directories
# Docker needs for its bind mounts, without forcing the user's
# PDFs or the SQLite database into version control.
/shared/*
!/shared/.gitkeep
/data/*
!/data/.gitkeep
/uploads/*
/.atl/
